title: Dwarf
content: A **dwarf planet** is a planetary-mass object that is neither a planet nor a satellite.

title: Terrestrial
content: A **terrestrial planet**, **telluric planet** or **rocky planet** is a planet that is composed primarily of silicate rocks or metals.

title: Gas Giant
content: A **gas giant** is a large planet that is not primarily composed of rock or other solid matter.
